OL,3,CWest Midlands police boss defends
OL,4,Cknife crime record after setting no
OL,5,Ctarget
OL,7,FThe Chief Constable of West Midlands
OL,8,FPolice, Craig Guildford, has defended
OL,9,Fhis approach to tackling knife crime,
OL,10,Finsisting he won't be setting a
OL,11,F"binary target" for reductions.
OL,13,F"My goal is to continue reducing and
OL,14,Fhave fewer victims. That's my goal and
OL,15,FI haven't set a binary target. It's a
OL,16,Freduction," he said.
