OL,3,CWest Midlands police boss defends
OL,4,Cknife crime record after setting no
OL,5,Ctarget
OL,7,FDespite the West Midlands still having
OL,8,Fthe second-highest rate of reported
OL,9,Fknife crime in the country, Guildford
OL,10,Finsists the force is making real
OL,11,Fprogress.
OL,13,FWhen asked if the West Midlands will
OL,14,Fever stop being the worst-hit area for
OL,15,Fknife crime outside London, Guildford
OL,16,Fpointed to recent improvements: "We
OL,17,Fwere the top in the country and we're
OL,18,Fnow not. The reason we're not is
OL,19,Fbecause we are reducing knife crime.
