OL,7,F"Knife-enabled robberies is down by
OL,8,Fover 50%... I have shared some of the
OL,9,Fwork that we've been doing in the West
OL,10,FMidlands with the public, force
OL,11,Fcolleagues and the Police Minister
OL,12,Fonly this week."
OL,14,FHe stressed that tackling knife crime
OL,15,Fremains a priority: "It is important
OL,16,Fthat the public understand that we
OL,17,Fwork very, very hard to reduce knife
OL,18,Fcrime.
