OL,7,F"Each knife crime is one too many.
OL,8,FWe've got a good operation to prevent
OL,9,Fknife crime and to investigate knife
OL,10,Fcrime.
OL,12,F"We invest in schools officers and,
OL,13,Fmost importantly, we try and put our
OL,14,Fresources in the right place at the
OL,15,Fright time.
