OL,3,CWest Midlands police boss defends
OL,4,Cknife crime record after setting no
OL,5,Ctarget
OL,7,F"Murders are down this year. That's
OL,8,Fthrough some very, very hard work and
OL,9,Fwe continually look at opportunities
OL,10,Fto reduce knife crime, particularly to
OL,11,Fswiftly arrest offenders and prevent
OL,12,Ffurther offences."
OL,14,FOver the past two years, homicides in
OL,15,Fthe West Midlands have dropped by a
OL,16,Fthird, while the number of arrests has
OL,17,Fdoubled. The force says this is why
OL,18,Fthey're opening new custody suites to
OL,19,Fmanage demand.
