OL,7,FBournville Police Station is the
OL,8,Flatest of three new processing centres
OL,9,Fto open, as West Midlands Police looks
OL,10,Fto improve how it handles offenders.
OL,12,FHowever, knife crime remains
OL,13,Fstubbornly high. In January, 12-year-
OL,14,Fold Leo Ross was stabbed to death
OL,15,Fwhile walking home from school in Hall
OL,16,FGreen.
OL,18,FA 14-year-old boy has been charged
OL,19,Fwith his murder.
