OL,7,FThe latest figures show a 6% drop in
OL,8,Freported knife crime in 2024. But the
OL,9,Fnumbers are still stark - nearly 3,500
OL,10,Fincidents in the West Midlands last
OL,11,Fyear involved a knife.
